comments: Valanciunas (MEM) makes marginal contact to the body of Hampton (ORL) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Brooks (MEM) extends his leg outward to initiate the marginal contact with Bacon (ORL) during his jump shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (ORL) and Valanciunas (MEM) briefly engage and separate in the post.
Valanciunas (MEM) hooks Carter Jr. (ORL) in the post.
Anderson (MEM) legally contests Wagner's (ORL) jump shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (ORL) avoids making contact and legally contests the driving shot attempt from Morant (MEM).
Wagner (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Brooks (MEM) firms up and abosorbs the contact.
Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Brooks (MEM) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Bacon (ORL) legally contests Brooks' (MEM) jump shot attempt.
Anderson (MEM) legally contests Anthony's (ORL) jump shot attempt.
